![Episode 153.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1605718609144-AQ2XBRET948SEU62BJ6U/Episode+153.jpg)

When Courtney Whitmore aka Stargirl first moved to Blue Valley, Nebraska, she thought she would die of boredom. Little did she know her life was in danger for other reasons! Stargirl, whose first season just concluded earlier this year, became a bright spot in an otherwise bleak 2020. The show manages to toe-the-line between adorable and dangerous as it introduces the Injustice Society to a whole new generation, whilst tackling some teen adversity at the same time. Grab your cosmic staff, put on your special goggles, and turn that hourglass over, us as we review one of the best things out of 2020, Stargirl Season 1! 

**Please** leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](../episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
